 Award Categories And Nominees|website=Soompi|language=en|access-date=2019-01-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hankookilbo.com/News/Read/201901232162337402|title='2019 \uac00\uc628\ucc28\ud2b8' \ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8, K-POP \uacf5\ud5cc\uc0c1 \"\ub9c8\uc74c\uc744 \uc6c0\uc9c1\uc774\ub294 \uc9c4\uc2ec\"|date=2019-01-23|website=\ud55c\uad6d\uc77c\ubcf4|language=ko|access-date=2019-01-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.etoday.co.kr/news/section/newsview.php?idxno=1714386|title=\u20182019 \uac00\uc628\ucc28\ud2b8\u2019 \uc5d1\uc18c\u2027\ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8, \u2018\uc62c\ud574\uc758 \uac00\uc218\uc0c1\u2019 \uc218\uc0c1\u2026\u201c\ud56d\uc0c1 \uac10\uc0ac\ud558\ub2e4\u201d|last=\uae30\uc0ac\uc785\ub825: 2019-01-23 20:52|date=2019-01-23|website=\uc774\ud22c\ub370\uc774|language=ko|access-date=2019-01-28}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| [[Golden Disc Awards]]\n| align=\"center\"| Digital Bonsang\n| {{won}}\n| align=\"center\"| <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mosen.mt.co.kr/article/G1111045288 |script-title=ko:\ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8\u00b7\uc544\uc774\uc720, \uace8\ub4e0\ub514\uc2a4\ud06c \ubcf8\uc0c1\u00b7\ub300\uc0c1 \ud6c4\ubcf4..2\ub144 \uc5f0\uc18d \ub300\uc0c1 \ub178\ub9b0\ub2e4|work=OSEN|last=Kang|first=Seojeong|date=December 7, 2018|language=ko|accessdate=December 8, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" | [[Teen Choice Awards]]\n| align=\"center\" | Choice Song: Group\n| {{Won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/teen-choice-awards-nominations-avengers-endgame-riverdale-1203247410/amp/|title=\u2018Avengers: Endgame,\u2019 \u2018Riverdale,\u2019 \u2018Aladdin\u2019 Top 2019 Teen Choice Award Nominations|last=Moreau|first=Jordan|date=June 19, 2019|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|url-status=live|access-date=September 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Year-end lists===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!Critic/Publication\n!List\n!Rank\n!Ref.\n|-\n|''Hypable''\n|rowspan=\"1\"|10 great K-Pop songs from 2018 to add to your end-of-year playlist\n|2\n|<ref>{{cite web |last1=Abramo |first1=Donya |title=10 great K-Pop songs from 2018 to add to your end-of-year playlist |url=https://www.hypable.com/best-k-pop-songs-2018/ |website=Hypable |accessdate=January 4, 2019 |date=December 30, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[The New York Times]]''\n|rowspan=\"1\"|The 65 Best Songs of 2018\n|31\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/12/06/arts/music/best-songs.html?action=click&module=RelatedLinks&pgtype=Article|title=The 65 Best Songs of 2018|work=[[The New York Times]]|last=Caramanica|first=Jon|date=December 6, 2018|accessdate=December 7, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Paper (magazine)|Paper]]''\n|rowspan=\"1\"|Top 20 K-Pop Songs of 2018\n|13\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.papermag.com/papers-top-20-k-pop-songs-of-2018-2624051281.html |title=PAPER's Top 20 K-Pop Songs of 2018 |last=Benjamin |first=Jeff |date=December 21, 2018 |website=[[Paper (magazine)|Paper]] |publisher=Paper Communications |access-date=December 28, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[YouTube|YouTube Rewind]]''\n|rowspan=\"1\"|Top 10 Most Popular Music Videos In Korea From 2018\n|2\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=003&aid=0008949420|title=Top 10 Most Popular Music Videos In Korea From 2018|work=[[YouTube]]|date=December 6, 2018|accessdate=December 7, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Rolling Stone]]''\n|rowspan=\"1\"|10 Best Music Videos of 2018\n|8\n|<ref name=\"RS Video\" />\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|''i-D''\n| align=\"center\"|everything that happened to k-pop in 2018\n| align=\"center\" {{N/A}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=everything that happened to k-pop in 2018 |url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/yw7kvv/k-pop-in-2018-bts-blackpink |website=[[Vice (magazine)|Vice]] |accessdate=January 8, 2019 |date=December 17, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|+Decade-end lists\n|-\n! Publication\n! Accolade\n! Rank / Year\n! class=\"unsortable\"