\ud761|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/144/0000553049|website=Naver|publisher=|accessdate=February 14, 2020 |language=Korean|date=May 18, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Radio shows===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:left;\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Network\n! Notes\n! Ref.\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2017\u20132019\n| ''Listen''\n| [[Educational Broadcasting System|EBS]]\n| DJ\n| <ref name = \"radio\"/>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{Main|List of awards and nominations received by Chungha}}\n{{See also|List of awards and nominations received by I.O.I}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Chungha}}\n* [http://mnh.eggpage.net/page/19798/gallery/4290 Chungha] at MNH Entertainment {{in lang|ko}}\n\n{{Chungha}}\n{{I.O.I}}\n{{Produce 101}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Singers from Seoul]]\n[[Category:South Korean female idols]]\n[[Category:South Korean female pop singers]]\n[[Category:21st-century South Korean singers]]\n[[Category:South Korean dance musicians]]\n[[Category:Produce 101 contestants]]\n[[Category:I.O.I members]]\n[[Category:King of Mask Singer contestants]]\n[[Category:21st-century women singers]]\n[[Category:Sejong University alumni]]\n", "text_old": "{{Other uses|Cheongha (disambiguation){{!}}Cheongha}}\n{{short description|South Korean singer}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Korean name|Kim}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name            = Chungha\n| image           = Chungha at Gaon Music Awards red carpet on January 8, 2020.png\n<!-- Please UPDATE THE ALT TEXT when you change an image. -->\n| alt             = Chungha looks forward in a checkered blouse against a white background\n| caption         = Chungha on January 8, 2020\n| image_size      = 225\n| native_name     = \uccad\ud558\n| native_name_lang= ko\n| birth_name      = Kim Chan-mi\n| birth_date      = {{birth date and age|1996|02|09}}\n| birth_place   